  "description": "A powerful ocean wave curls dramatically as surfers attempt to ride it. The wave is a deep blue with a frothy white crest, exhibiting significant turbulence and spray. Several surfers are visible on the face of the wave, appearing small against its immense scale. In the background, a coastal town is nestled against rolling hills, with buildings and vegetation visible. The scene suggests a warm, sunny day with clear visibility. There are also other surfers dotted further out in the water.",
